{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":972,"text":"Paul Krugman, the Nobel Prize\n[winner] in economics, once wrote:"},{"time":6929,"text":"\"Productivity is not everything,\nbut in the long run,"},{"time":12349,"text":"it is almost everything.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":16062,"text":"So this is serious."},{"time":18214,"text":"There are not that many things on earth\nthat are \"almost everything.\""},{"time":24138,"text":"Productivity is the principal driver\nof the prosperity of a society."},{"time":31560,"text":"So we have a problem."},{"time":33837,"text":"In the largest European economies,"},{"time":36630,"text":"productivity used to grow\nfive percent per annum"},{"time":39804,"text":"in the '50s, '60s, early '70s."},{"time":42943,"text":"From '73 to '83: three percent per annum."},{"time":46995,"text":"From '83 to '95: two percent per annum."},{"time":50308,"text":"Since 1995: less than\none percent per annum."},{"time":55042,"text":"The same profile in Japan."},{"time":58115,"text":"The same profile in the US,"},{"time":61009,"text":"despite a momentary rebound 15 years ago,"},{"time":66366,"text":"and despite all\nthe technological innovations"},{"time":69754,"text":"around us: the Internet, the information,"},{"time":72357,"text":"the new information\nand communication technologies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76155,"text":"When productivity grows\nthree percent per annum,"},{"time":80758,"text":"you double the standard of living\nevery generation."},{"time":85169,"text":"Every generation is twice\nas well-off as its parents'."},{"time":90686,"text":"When it grows one percent per annum,"},{"time":94036,"text":"it takes three generations\nto double the standard of living."},{"time":97687,"text":"And in this process, many people\nwill be less well-off than their parents."},{"time":103505,"text":"They will have less of everything:"},{"time":106043,"text":"smaller roofs, or perhaps no roof at all,"},{"time":110645,"text":"less access to education, to vitamins,\nto antibiotics, to vaccination --"},{"time":117068,"text":"to everything."},{"time":119502,"text":"Think of all the problems\nthat we're facing at the moment."},{"time":126347,"text":"All."},{"time":128692,"text":"Chances are that they are rooted\nin the productivity crisis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135226,"text":"Why this crisis?"},{"time":138438,"text":"Because the basic tenets\nabout efficiency --"},{"time":143937,"text":"effectiveness in organizations,\nin management --"},{"time":148772,"text":"have become counterproductive\nfor human efforts."},{"time":153539,"text":"Everywhere in public services --\nin companies, in the way we work,"},{"time":157729,"text":"the way we innovate, invest --\ntry to learn to work better."},{"time":162954,"text":"Take the holy trinity of efficiency:"},{"time":168805,"text":"clarity, measurement, accountability."},{"time":175870,"text":"They make human efforts derail."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179650,"text":"There are two ways\nto look at it, to prove it."},{"time":183746,"text":"One, the one I prefer,"},{"time":186436,"text":"is rigorous, elegant, nice -- math."},{"time":192593,"text":"But the full math version\ntakes a little while,"},{"time":195880,"text":"so there is another one."},{"time":197699,"text":"It is to look at a relay race."},{"time":200697,"text":"This is what we will do today."},{"time":202389,"text":"It's a bit more animated, more visual\nand also faster -- it's a race."},{"time":209572,"text":"Hopefully, it's faster."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210890,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":212278,"text":"World championship final -- women."},{"time":217260,"text":"Eight teams in the final."},{"time":219395,"text":"The fastest team is the US team."},{"time":223129,"text":"They have the fastest women on earth."},{"time":226153,"text":"They are the favorite team to win."},{"time":228952,"text":"Notably, if you compare them\nto an average team,"},{"time":233166,"text":"say, the French team,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":234564,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":236175,"text":"based on their best performances\nin the 100-meter race,"},{"time":241394,"text":"if you add the individual times\nof the US runners,"},{"time":247187,"text":"they arrive at the finish line\n3.2 meters ahead of the French team."},{"time":254438,"text":"And this year, the US team\nis in great shape."},{"time":258034,"text":"Based on their best performance this year,"},{"time":260444,"text":"they arrive 6.4 meters\nahead of the French team,"},{"time":265373,"text":"based on the data."},{"time":267274,"text":"We are going to look at the race."},{"time":268877,"text":"At some point you will see,\ntowards the end,"},{"time":271324,"text":"that Torri Edwards,\nthe fourth US runner, is ahead."},{"time":277654,"text":"Not surprising -- this year she got\nthe gold medal in the 100-meter race."},{"time":284167,"text":"And by the way, Chryste Gaines,\nthe second runner in the US team,"},{"time":289133,"text":"is the fastest woman on earth."},{"time":291794,"text":"So, there are 3.5 billion women on earth."},{"time":297890,"text":"Where are the two fastest? On the US team."},{"time":301087,"text":"And the two other runners\non the US team are not bad, either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304384,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":306124,"text":"So clearly, the US team has won\nthe war for talent."},{"time":312391,"text":"But behind, the average team\nis trying to catch up."},{"time":316396,"text":"Let's watch the race."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318300,"text":"(Video: French sportscasters narrate race)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":366886,"text":"(Video: Race narration ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":370112,"text":"Yves Morieux: So what happened?"},{"time":371631,"text":"The fastest team did not win;\nthe slower one did."},{"time":376809,"text":"By the way, I hope you appreciate"},{"time":378770,"text":"the deep historical research I did\nto make the French look good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":389485,"text":"But let's not exaggerate --\nit's not archeology, either."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393928,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":395933,"text":"But why?"},{"time":397123,"text":"Because of cooperation."},{"time":398687,"text":"When you hear this sentence:"},{"time":400545,"text":"\"Thanks to cooperation, the whole\nis worth more than the sum of the parts.\""},{"time":405707,"text":"This is not poetry;\nthis is not philosophy."},{"time":409046,"text":"This is math."},{"time":411196,"text":"Those who carry the baton are slower,"},{"time":414500,"text":"but their baton is faster."},{"time":416848,"text":"Miracle of cooperation:"},{"time":419057,"text":"it multiplies energy,\nintelligence in human efforts."},{"time":424361,"text":"It is the essence of human efforts:"},{"time":427360,"text":"how we work together, how each effort\ncontributes to the efforts of others."},{"time":434017,"text":"With cooperation,\nwe can do more with less."}]},{"cues":[{"time":437788,"text":"Now, what happens to cooperation\nwhen the holy grail --"},{"time":443360,"text":"the holy trinity, even --"},{"time":445822,"text":"of clarity, measurement, accountability --"},{"time":452067,"text":"appears?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454952,"text":"Clarity."},{"time":456128,"text":"Management reports are full of complaints\nabout the lack of clarity."},{"time":461424,"text":"Compliance audits,\nconsultants' diagnostics."},{"time":466490,"text":"We need more clarity, we need\nto clarify the roles, the processes."},{"time":472092,"text":"It is as though the runners\non the team were saying,"},{"time":476132,"text":"\"Let's be clear -- where does my role\nreally start and end?"},{"time":482938,"text":"Am I supposed to run for 95 meters,\n96, 97...?\""},{"time":487794,"text":"It's important, let's be clear."},{"time":490885,"text":"If you say 97, after 97 meters,"},{"time":493915,"text":"people will drop the baton, whether\nthere is someone to take it or not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":499145,"text":"Accountability."},{"time":501084,"text":"We are constantly trying\nto put accountability"},{"time":504558,"text":"in someone's hands."},{"time":506559,"text":"Who is accountable for this process?"},{"time":509156,"text":"We need somebody accountable\nfor this process."},{"time":512634,"text":"So in the relay race,\nsince passing the baton is so important,"},{"time":517119,"text":"then we need somebody\nclearly accountable for passing the baton."},{"time":521786,"text":"So between each runner,"},{"time":523989,"text":"now we will have a new dedicated athlete,"},{"time":528737,"text":"clearly dedicated to taking\nthe baton from one runner,"},{"time":533306,"text":"and passing it to the next runner."},{"time":536284,"text":"And we will have at least two like that."},{"time":540381,"text":"Well, will we, in that case, win the race?"},{"time":547903,"text":"That I don't know, but for sure,"},{"time":549928,"text":"we would have a clear interface,"},{"time":553222,"text":"a clear line of accountability."},{"time":555890,"text":"We will know who to blame."},{"time":558834,"text":"But we'll never win the race."},{"time":561099,"text":"If you think about it,\nwe pay more attention"},{"time":566110,"text":"to knowing who to blame in case we fail,"},{"time":570289,"text":"than to creating\nthe conditions to succeed."},{"time":575384,"text":"All the human intelligence\nput in organization design --"},{"time":578771,"text":"urban structures, processing systems --"},{"time":581580,"text":"what is the real goal?"},{"time":584347,"text":"To have somebody guilty in case they fail."},{"time":588499,"text":"We are creating\norganizations able to fail,"},{"time":593410,"text":"but in a compliant way,"},{"time":596411,"text":"with somebody clearly\naccountable when we fail."},{"time":599877,"text":"And we are quite effective\nat that -- failing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":604892,"text":"Measurement."},{"time":606674,"text":"What gets measured gets done."},{"time":608126,"text":"Look, to pass the baton,\nyou have to do it at the right time,"},{"time":612541,"text":"in the right hand, at the right speed."},{"time":615457,"text":"But to do that, you have to put\nenergy in your arm."},{"time":618040,"text":"This energy that is in your arm\nwill not be in your legs."},{"time":621491,"text":"It will come at the expense\nof your measurable speed."},{"time":625367,"text":"You have to shout early enough\nto the next runner"},{"time":628844,"text":"when you will pass the baton,\nto signal that you are arriving,"},{"time":632179,"text":"so that the next runner\ncan prepare, can anticipate."},{"time":635408,"text":"And you have to shout loud."},{"time":638182,"text":"But the blood, the energy\nthat will be in your throat"},{"time":642179,"text":"will not be in your legs."},{"time":643603,"text":"Because you know, there are\neight people shouting at the same time."},{"time":647383,"text":"So you have to recognize the voice\nof your colleague."},{"time":650372,"text":"You cannot say, \"Is it you?\""},{"time":652570,"text":"Too late!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":653748,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":654978,"text":"Now, let's look at the race\nin slow motion,"},{"time":659978,"text":"and concentrate on the third runner."},{"time":662550,"text":"Look at where she allocates her efforts,"},{"time":666997,"text":"her energy, her attention."},{"time":670878,"text":"Not all in her legs -- that would\nbe great for her own speed --"},{"time":674046,"text":"but in also in her throat,\narm, eye, brain."},{"time":677560,"text":"That makes a difference in whose legs?"},{"time":680314,"text":"In the legs of the next runner."},{"time":682728,"text":"But when the next runner runs super-fast,"},{"time":685586,"text":"is it because she made a super effort,"},{"time":687738,"text":"or because of the way\nthe third runner passed the baton?"},{"time":691403,"text":"There is no metric on earth\nthat will give us the answer."},{"time":696310,"text":"And if we reward people on the basis\nof their measurable performance,"},{"time":700845,"text":"they will put their energy,\ntheir attention, their blood"},{"time":703923,"text":"in what can get measured -- in their legs."},{"time":706581,"text":"And the baton will fall and slow down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709534,"text":"To cooperate is not a super effort,"},{"time":712130,"text":"it is how you allocate your effort."},{"time":715280,"text":"It is to take a risk,"},{"time":717144,"text":"because you sacrifice\nthe ultimate protection"},{"time":721398,"text":"granted by objectively measurable\nindividual performance."},{"time":728516,"text":"It is to make a super difference\nin the performance of others,"},{"time":732417,"text":"with whom we are compared."},{"time":734757,"text":"It takes being stupid to cooperate, then."},{"time":737551,"text":"And people are not stupid;\nthey don't cooperate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740738,"text":"You know, clarity, accountability,\nmeasurement were OK"},{"time":745902,"text":"when the world was simpler."},{"time":748929,"text":"But business has become much more complex."},{"time":751977,"text":"With my teams, we have measured"},{"time":754032,"text":"the evolution of complexity in business."},{"time":757080,"text":"It is much more demanding today\nto attract and retain customers,"},{"time":762707,"text":"to build advantage on a global scale,"},{"time":766042,"text":"to create value."},{"time":768691,"text":"And the more business gets complex,"},{"time":771472,"text":"the more, in the name of clarity,\naccountability, measurement"},{"time":776797,"text":"we multiply structures,\nprocesses, systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781083,"text":"You know, this drive for clarity\nand accountability triggers"},{"time":785916,"text":"a counterproductive multiplication\nof interfaces, middle offices,"},{"time":791295,"text":"coordinators that do not only\nmobilize people and resources,"},{"time":796356,"text":"but that also add obstacles."},{"time":799276,"text":"And the more complicated the organization,"},{"time":803870,"text":"the more difficult it is to understand\nwhat is really happening."},{"time":807547,"text":"So we need summaries, proxies, reports,"},{"time":812991,"text":"key performance indicators, metrics."},{"time":816315,"text":"So people put their energy\nin what can get measured,"},{"time":821051,"text":"at the expense of cooperation."},{"time":823170,"text":"And as performance deteriorates,"},{"time":825726,"text":"we add even more structure,\nprocess, systems."},{"time":828879,"text":"People spend their time in meetings,"},{"time":831735,"text":"writing reports they have\nto do, undo and redo."},{"time":836289,"text":"Based on our analysis,\nteams in these organizations"},{"time":839735,"text":"spend between 40 and 80 percent\nof their time wasting their time,"},{"time":845930,"text":"but working harder and harder,\nlonger and longer,"},{"time":849947,"text":"on less and less value-adding activities."},{"time":854242,"text":"This is what is killing productivity,"},{"time":856576,"text":"what makes people suffer at work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":859226,"text":"Our organizations are wasting\nhuman intelligence."},{"time":863787,"text":"They have turned against human efforts."},{"time":868673,"text":"When people don't cooperate,"},{"time":871587,"text":"don't blame their mindsets,\ntheir mentalities, their personality --"},{"time":876006,"text":"look at the work situations."},{"time":879125,"text":"Is it really in their personal interest\nto cooperate or not,"},{"time":883398,"text":"if, when they cooperate,\nthey are individually worse off?"},{"time":887914,"text":"Why would they cooperate?"},{"time":889922,"text":"When we blame personalities"},{"time":893538,"text":"instead of the clarity,\nthe accountability, the measurement,"},{"time":899720,"text":"we add injustice to ineffectiveness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":905654,"text":"We need to create organizations"},{"time":907591,"text":"in which it becomes individually useful\nfor people to cooperate."},{"time":912807,"text":"Remove the interfaces,\nthe middle offices --"},{"time":917626,"text":"all these complicated\ncoordination structures."},{"time":921573,"text":"Don't look for clarity; go for fuzziness."},{"time":925977,"text":"Fuzziness overlaps."},{"time":929244,"text":"Remove most of the quantitative metrics\nto assess performance."},{"time":934200,"text":"Speed the \"what.\""},{"time":936414,"text":"Look at cooperation, the \"how.\""},{"time":939255,"text":"How did you pass the baton?"},{"time":940880,"text":"Did you throw it,\nor did you pass it effectively?"},{"time":946569,"text":"Am I putting my energy\nin what can get measured --"},{"time":952651,"text":"my legs, my speed --\nor in passing the baton?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":956810,"text":"You, as leaders, as managers,"},{"time":961177,"text":"are you making it individually useful\nfor people to cooperate?"},{"time":968205,"text":"The future of our organizations,"},{"time":971367,"text":"our companies, our societies"},{"time":975184,"text":"hinges on your answer to these questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":981035,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":982240,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}